  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NoteItem
  noteTitle: Test
  fullText: "<b>Day <color=red>#14</color></b>\n\nThey told me the treatment would
    help. They lied. Every time I close my eyes, I hear the scratching inside the
    walls.\n\rIf anyone finds this... tell Sarah I\u2019m sorry. I tried to stay
    sane, but the shadows in this hallway... they have teeth.. \n<b>HELP ME.</b>"
